actual.comment:
As part of regional networking, Customs and Enforcement issues were particularly discussed:


o	During the thematic meeting on Montreal protocol and the new Customs Union, organised by one of the project countries (Belarus) in 2014 in Minsk. UNEP-sponsored Art 5 countries attended this meeting and exchanged experience on HCFC control options with open borders;

o	(previously reported) During the joint meeting of Customs officers co-organised with UNEP in Sarajevo on the occasion of the Regional Network Meeting in May 2014. Participation was proposed to customs administrations of the 4 countries in the project (although in the end Uzbekistan's customs could not attend).

